g.text: abc # Matches any string that starts with "abc"
# Matches any string that ends with "abc"
# Matches the string "abc" and nothing else
b # Matches any string containing "a", any character, then
# Matches two or more consecutive "a" characters
# Matches zero or more consecutive "a" characters
# Matches one or more consecutive "a" characters
b # Positive lookbehind: matches "b" that is preceded by "
b # Negative lookbehind: matches "b" that is not preceded
# Positive lookahead: matches "a" that is followed by "b
# Negative lookahead: matches "a" that is not followed b
